liveDescNotEmptyNew.message: The live session name should be between 1 and 500 characters

enterClassroomNameErr.message: Session name must not be more than 50 characters

confirmDeleteClassroom.message: Deleting a classroom session will delete all the classroom activities launched in the session. Are you sure you want to delete?

copyClassroomTip.message: (Duplicated activities are inactive. You can activate these activities after the session starts. Roll Call and Random Pick activities cannot be duplicated.)

classsroomHeadTips1.message: For face-face classroom sessions, the teacher can launch various activities on (or cast the activities to) a big screen to facilitate learning. The course sessions, activities, and activity data are all tracked and stored in ULearning. The data can be used/analyzed by the teacher/school for different purposes.

cannotView.message: Previews are not currently supported for the past activities

ltiErrorTip.message: The page is not accessible, contact your administrator to check the app configuration.

menuManageTip.message: Course admins can hide/show the menus here, or change the course home page. Hidden menus are invisible (some individual menus are invisible to students only). It applies to ULearning App. If the menu is set as the course home page, the course landing is the menu.

fixMenuTip.message: Fixed menus (visible only to course admins) cannot be hidden

hideForStu.message: Hiding applies to the student side only

hideIndexTip.message: The course home page cannot be hidden. To hide this menu, first set another menu as the course home page.

clickToGetMoreApp.message: Click the button on the right to add more app

appSupportTip.message: Support PC only for teachers, while support both PC and ULearning App for students.
